text: Jamal Ahmed Al-Doseri (born 1 January 1970) is a Bahraini former cyclist. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Bahraini male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Bahrain Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
